{"id": 959, "genre": 1001, "title": "你受不了机场的哪些设计？", "description": "“我难受地坐在登机口，等待转接航班，精疲力竭却十分清醒，只希望自己不要分到机舱里的一个中间座位。”——CHRIS HOLBROOK（题图来自：Marion Fayolle）", "record_count": 3571, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183637J6Uw2MP7dHNaE5jt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-29T11:03:12Z", "options": [{"id": 71680, "content": "远机位需要坐摆渡车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125119}, {"id": 71682, "content": "提着行李，死也走不到登机口，过关小卡片要不要放的这么隐蔽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589984}, {"id": 71684, "content": "没有24小时商店", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114717}, {"id": 71685, "content": "摆渡车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498373}, {"id": 72965, "content": "走了半天找不到点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517933}, {"id": 71686, "content": "走到登机口太远太远太远太远…………", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 503290}, {"id": 71942, "content": "厕所没纸。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127182}, {"id": 71687, "content": "等托运行李最郁闷！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590020}, {"id": 71688, "content": "大冬天坐摆渡车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478933}, {"id": 72467, "content": "味道不好闻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591593}, {"id": 73494, "content": "手机充电插座有的坏了..充电要站着...站着要好久...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363292}, {"id": 72727, "content": "没有绿色通道（急客通道），工作人员让我自己和排在前面的乘客商量看能否加塞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589870}, {"id": 71705, "content": "安检口排老长队了，仍不会多开放几个", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590044}, {"id": 71963, "content": "好不容易找到插座发现全被周围站坐卧靠墙的人们包围", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574944}, {"id": 73502, "content": "贵宾室", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572478}, {"id": 74275, "content": "沒有人認為深圳機場對密集恐懼症患者特別不友好嗎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575846}, {"id": 72229, "content": "看到自己的行李被粗暴的扔进车里…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591216}, {"id": 71719, "content": "表示没坐过，不知道生病的耳膜会不会受得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 587907}, {"id": 72744, "content": "催促登机只设在登机口广播，试问如果我在登机口还看不到听不到吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589870}, {"id": 73000, "content": "做个飞机就像是在这世间轮回了一遭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485496}, {"id": 70953, "content": "转机时候睡眼惺忪地走了15分钟才走到航站楼的另一端", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 70954, "content": "转机厅灯光亮得让人睡不着，但读书又不够亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 70955, "content": "下雨天还要坐摆渡车，崩溃", "image": null, "praise_count": 258, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 70956, "content": "椅子太硬，扶手太靠近，转机想要睡一会只能躺在地上", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 70957, "content": "没有给笔记本或手机充电的插口", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 71725, "content": "每次去取行李的地方都会走很久，但是每次都会发现无论走的多慢，行李都会比你慢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572022}, {"id": 70958, "content": "没wifi，wifi不好用", "image": null, "praise_count": 425, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 71983, "content": "深圳机场有着无数的草点...别的机场提前一个小时那么深圳机场要多加半小时给你走路，我靠  赶脚走了几个公交站，还有飞机延误大冬天那么冷居然没有毯子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569826}, {"id": 73017, "content": "说得好像我去过机场样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436756}, {"id": 75065, "content": "国际航班位子这么小，晚上6个小时简直度秒如年…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235046}, {"id": 71738, "content": "国内机场很多设计都不人性化，应该学学新加坡樟宜机场。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578298}, {"id": 71994, "content": "出行李口行李都是被扔出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590331}, {"id": 71995, "content": "一份饭150", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485944}, {"id": 74044, "content": "听到机场哪里都觉得不合理！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 73282, "content": "国内机场舍不得开灯吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165066}, {"id": 73283, "content": "视觉导向系统杂乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165066}, {"id": 72260, "content": "机场本身就是个设计问题！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209243}, {"id": 80207, "content": "WiFi要登录?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 616093}, {"id": 73299, "content": "登机没有廊桥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592309}, {"id": 72291, "content": "安检队排得太长～～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236321}, {"id": 76391, "content": "登机口离安检处太远太远", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 505994}, {"id": 72040, "content": "拿登机牌还要找航空公司，好累啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522442}, {"id": 71792, "content": "安检太乱了，脱衣服不说，每次都把电脑手机平板拿出来，还不给我轻拿轻放。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187879}, {"id": 71796, "content": "候机厅的椅子永远比需求量少2/3。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573836}, {"id": 73595, "content": "星巴克放在安检口外面真的大丈夫么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194226}, {"id": 145792, "content": "性冷淡风格的装修", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732330}, {"id": 72070, "content": "有些机场竟然不是24小时的！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 192556}, {"id": 71816, "content": "机场有设计吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396267}, {"id": 75403, "content": "各个航班办登机牌距离太远", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593207}, {"id": 78987, "content": "太平，么手感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569570}]}